{"tid":1462620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人少就宣傳 人多就會自然停飛 不割蓆不指責","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:19:41.000Z","uid":23991,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"126fb8b977216055d714ec74f8a38e59551c4480","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"記住大家的目標係一樣<br />\n我地要逼到呢個垃圾政府回應<br />\n向外國勢力文宣又好<br />\n搞停機場又好<br />\n大家都係想逼到政府回應<br />\n槍口一致對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多po互屌<br />\n驚賊公布左卧底<br />\n我知大家依加覺得一街係鬼<br />\n但要記得我地點樣捱到今日<br />\n我地要一直檢討進步<br />\n唔好第一反應就屌鬼<br />\n對外對內都記得要有公關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前線手足唔夠人 推車封路<br />\n你地要屌的 全部同我入曬機場屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地人夠多的 一齊移走啲車 靠人數塞停機場<br />\n<br />\nbe humble, my friend"},{"pid":"8fc5242bd98c7051d45439e4a036d38257948827","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d361fc2745327a41727f5ade68bf525a8614ce0","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c2238598301cabe58666fd4c007411e3d3cae6","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"83cbacdd19f20fa5a9691e6a4e42e45025944cb8","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"70be8bb17cb8a7a95280887ce1815fcf9a625176","tid":1462620,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa4cc96fb09dde984926bb386c5019d14e3c6587","tid":1462620,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dis